								</svg>
							</a>
						</div>
					</div>
					
					<div>
						<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Resources</h3>
						<ul class="space-y-2 text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-300">
							<li><a href="https://github.com/thedaviddias/llms.txt-hub" class="hover:text-primary-600 dark:hover:text-primary-400">LLMS.txt Hub</a></li>
							<li><a href="https://searchengineland.com/llms-txt-proposed-standard-453676" class="hover:text-primary-600 dark:hover:text-primary-400">LLMS.txt Standard</a></li>
							<li><a href="https://github.com/example/llms-explorer/issues" class="hover:text-primary-600 dark:hover:text-primary-400">Report Issues</a></li>
							<li><a href="https://github.com/example/llms-explorer/blob/main/CONTRIBUTING.md" class="hover:text-primary-600 dark:hover:text-primary-400">Contribute</a></li>
						</ul>
					</div>
					
					<div>
						<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Legal</h3>
						<ul class="space-y-2 text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-300">
							<li><a href="/privacy" class="hover:text-primary-600 dark:hover:text-primary-400">Privacy Policy</a></li>
							<li><a href="/terms" class="hover:text-primary-600 dark:hover:text-primary-400">Terms of Service</a></li>
							<li><a href="/cookies" class="hover:text-primary-600 dark:hover:text-primary-400">Cookie Policy</a></li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>
				
				<div class="border-t border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-700 mt-8 pt-8 text-center text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-400">
					<p>&copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} LLMS.txt Explorer. All rights reserved.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</footer>
	</body>
</html>
